                            &lt;p&gt;I like this format for documenting the activities - has anyone started to do this for the other activities list in the &lt;a href=&quot;http://coderetreat.org/facilitating/activity-catalog?&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;http://coderetreat.org/facilitating/activity-catalog?&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
