&lt;p&gt;So far so good, and facilitating has been a great new challenge with its own rewards!&lt;/p&gt;                    </summary>

                                            <content type="html">
                            &lt;p&gt;We&#039;re doing this mute style right now. For those who plan to try it in the next session, be sure to allow some extra setup time.  It took pairs several minutes to get their pairing setup worked out before we could officially go silent.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;So far so good, and facilitating has been a great new challenge with its own rewards!&lt;/p&gt;                        </content>
                    
